# Loop harness (NanoGraph)

For non-trivial work in this repo:

1. Run `./scripts/harness-session-start.sh` before planning or implementing.
2. Read `.harness-data/loop_state.json`, `.harness-data/product_proof_queue.json`, and `.harness-data/memory/summary.md`.
3. Invoke **`nanograph-loop-driver`** before substantial work (unless user waives).
4. Apply state updates by editing `loop_state.json` via the patch contract in `harness-quickstart` (no external agency daemon).
5. Do not change `NGB-V0.md` or `tools/**` for substantial work without `artifacts.spec_path` set in loop state.

See `docs/specs/AGENT-HARNESS.md`.
